  ('en', 'Gin', 'Under what king has gin become the English national drink ?', 'William III', 'Frédéric-Henri', 'Louis II', 'Willem-Alexander', '2', 'Gin became the English national drink when William III of Orange became in 1689 King of England, Scotland and Ireland.', ''),
