  ('en', 'Gin', 'In which manga is one of the main heroes nicknamed Gin ?', '« Detective Conan »', '« Robotboy »', '« ThunderCats »', '« Ben 10 »', '3', 'Gin and Vodka were the first members to appear when they forced Shinichi Kudo to take Apotoxin 4869.', ''),
