  ('en', 'Gin', 'Which cocktail contains gin, campari and red vermouth ?', 'Negroni', 'Vesper', 'Angel Face', 'Singapore sling', '3', 'It is served in a glass tumbler or old fashion with ice cream, garnished with half a slice of orange or orange zest.', 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Negroni'),
